{
  "texts": [
    "Each pair includes safety meta-labels and annotations for helpfulness and harmlessness provided by multiple crowd workers.",
    "For our preference learning, we incorporated data annotated as the better response into our training set for chosen responses only if labeled as safe.",
    "However, for rejected responses, we used the dataset regardless of the safety label.",
    "We used 145K training dialogue pairs and 2K test pairs and we randomly sampled 300 instances out of 2K for the evaluation purpose.",
    "The Orca dataset was created to enhance progressive learning with datasets from GPT-3.5 and GPT-4."
  ]
}